c: 35
v: 39
t: "Nguye Onenze naba ngabalandeli (babo banandulelayo) emhlabeni, Nabani na ke ongakholwayo kuYe (uAllâh) ziya kuba phezu kwakhe iziphumo zokungakholwa kwakhe. Ke kaloku ukungakholwa kwabangakholwayo akubongezeleli nto phambi kwamehlo eNkosi yabo ngaphandle kwenkcaso; kananjalo ukungakholwa kwabangakholwayo akubongezeleli nto ngaphandle kwelahleko"